#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.sinc.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.sinc"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:1 of
msgid "Return the sinc function."
msgstr "返回 sinc 函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:3 of
msgid "The sinc function is :math:`\\\\sin(\\\\pi x)/(\\\\pi x)`."
msgstr "sinc 函数为 :math:`\\\\sin(\\\\pi x)/(\\\\pi x)`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:5 of
msgid ""
"Tensor (possibly multi-dimensional) of values for which to to calculate "
"``sinc(x)``."
msgstr "用于计算 ``sinc(x)`` 的（可能是多维的）张量值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:9 of
msgid "**out** -- ``sinc(x)``, which has the same shape as the input."
msgstr "**out** -- ``sinc(x)``，其形状与输入相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:13 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:14 of
msgid "``sinc(0)`` is the limit value 1."
msgstr "``sinc(0)`` 的极限值为 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:16 of
msgid "The name sinc is short for \"sine cardinal\" or \"sinus cardinalis\"."
msgstr "sinc 是 \"sine cardinal\" 或 \"sinus cardinalis\" 的简称。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:18 of
msgid ""
"The sinc function is used in various signal processing applications, "
"including in anti-aliasing, in the construction of a Lanczos resampling "
"filter, and in interpolation."
msgstr ""
"sinc 函数用于各种信号处理应用中，包括抗混叠、Lanczos 重采样滤波器的构建"
"以及插值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:22 of
msgid ""
"For bandlimited interpolation of discrete-time signals, the ideal "
"interpolation kernel is proportional to the sinc function."
msgstr "对于离散时间信号的带限插值，理想的插值核与 sinc 函数成比例。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:26 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:27 of
msgid ""
"Weisstein, Eric W. \"Sinc Function.\" From MathWorld--A Wolfram Web "
"Resource. http://mathworld.wolfram.com/SincFunction.html"
msgstr ""
"Weisstein, Eric W. \"Sinc Function.\" 来自 MathWorld--Wolfram 网络资源。"
"http://mathworld.wolfram.com/SincFunction.html"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinc.sinc:29 of
msgid "Wikipedia, \"Sinc function\", http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sinc_function"
msgstr "维基百科，\"Sinc 函数\"，http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sinc_function"

